Title: Fix missing confirm dialog on editing used tag ID
Class: fix
Compatible: comp
Component: multisite
Date: 1619163636
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

If tag IDs were changed that are already in use by some folder, hosts or rules,
there was no confirm dialog to fix the affected objects. The changes were
silently skipped.

